# CLAUDE.md (Example)

## User Preferences

- Response language: Korean (or your language)
- Auto commit: commit + push on success
- Task-based workflow: use TaskCreate/TaskUpdate for all requests

## Telegram Notifications (Optional)

Set environment variables instead of hardcoding:

```bash
export TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN="your-bot-token"
export TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID="your-chat-id"
```

## Architecture Principles

- Auto dispatch: automatically select orchestrator based on task size
- Error recovery: bug-fixer auto-invocation (max 3 retries with strategy rotation)

## Security

- Never commit API keys, tokens, or passwords
- `.env`, `settings.local.json` must be in .gitignore
